{"ANTRAL":[{"def":"Relating to an antrum.","pos":""}],"ANTRORSE":[{"def":"Forward or upward in direction.","pos":""}],"ANTROVERT":[{"def":"To bend forward.","pos":""}],"ANTRUM":[{"def":"A cavern or cavity, esp.","pos":""}],"ANTRUSTION":[{"def":"A vassal or voluntary follower of Frankish princes in their enterprises.","pos":""}]}